{"tid":1615022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉危為機]其實有冇諗過呢個係民間自衛隊既契機","createTime":"2019-10-03T03:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T22:59:44.000Z","uid":442,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72aba69bd75af69556883bba01b2098582e405e1","tid":1615022,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:14:57.000Z","msg":"意為打爛商舖好爽，實際上瀨晒嘢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614658\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614658</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n只要手足快過狗出黎清場，只要d 黑狗驚我地<br />\n我地就係出師有名，正式保護民眾既義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先各位當區街坊要有自衛隊意識，一收到黃店被襲消息後馬上black bloc 到場，有黑打黑，無黑就收集証據，包括cctv 同黑狗特徵，之後就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係一個非常好既機會架空狗隊職能，進而令勇武手足加夠exp 打大佬之日使用<br />\n<br />\n和理非或後排觀眾可以提供黑狗去向或轉職至民間自衛隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"d34d808819fcf0fdb5d3578174c6fe5cd56ca504","tid":1615022,"uid":26419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:15:39.000Z","msg":"點拎cctv先"},{"pid":"a4e867238c13092767a9082a92a7c6efc5d7c9ff","tid":1615022,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d34d808819fcf0fdb5d3578174c6fe5cd56ca504","tid":1615022,"uid":26419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:15:39.000Z","msg":"點拎cctv先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:16:04.000Z","msg":"店主提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以要係黃店"},{"pid":"7e431afbbf8a6868f28d76d0523a09e2403c29f5","tid":1615022,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:16:34.000Z","msg":"支持民衛"},{"pid":"013a7124ad09c94602fd888f1ee393f31cbebf1e","tid":1615022,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco